<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <titleGet Your Detailed HubSpot Audit Report</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .container { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        label { display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold; }
        input[type="text"], input[type="email"] { width: 100%; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 16px; }
        .btn { background: #ff7a59; color: white; padding: 12px 25px; border: none; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 16px; width: 100%; }
        .benefits { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .benefits ul { margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px; }
        .benefits li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        <h1>Get Your Detailed HubSpot Audit Report</h1>
        <p>Your overall score: <strong style="color: #ff7a59; font-size: 1.2em;"><%= overallScore %>%</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>Unlock Your Personalized Action Plan</h2>
        
        <div class="benefits">
            <p><strong>By providing your email, you'll receive:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>ðŸ“Š <strong>Detailed PDF Report</strong> with section-by-section analysis</li>
                <li>ðŸŽ¯ <strong>Personalized Recommendations</strong> based on your score</li>
                <li>ðŸš€ <strong>Actionable Steps</strong> to improve your HubSpot usage</li>
                <li>ðŸ“ˆ <strong>Benchmark Data</strong> comparing you to industry standards</li>
                <li>ðŸ”§ <strong>Priority Support</strong> for HubSpot optimization</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <form action="/audit/save-lead" method="POST">
            <input type="hidden" name="overallScore" value="<%= overallScore %>">
            <input type="hidden" name="sectionScores" value="<%= JSON.stringify(sectionScores) %>">
            <input type="hidden" name="totalAchieved" value="<%= totalAchieved %>">
            <input type="hidden" name="totalPossible" value="<%= totalPossible %>">
            <input type="hidden" name="answers" value="<%= JSON.stringify(answers) %>">
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email">Email Address *</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="first_name">First Name</label>
                <input type="text" id="first_name" name="first_name">
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="last_name">Last Name</label>
                <input type="text" id="last_name" name="last_name">
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="company">Company</label>
                <input type="text" id="company" name="company">
            </div>
            
            <button type="submit" class="btn">Get My Detailed Report</button>
            
            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #666;">
                We respect your privacy. Unsubscribe at any time.
            </p>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>